s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/30293/', '', 'Azelastine, Ketotifen', 'Methotrimeprazine, Promazine, Pimavanserin, Amisulpride, Triflupromazine', 1767369485);
