hether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/30331/', '', 'Aducanumab', 'Amisulpride, Cariprazine, Lurasidone', 1767369485);
